id: pm-jpfc
title: Release @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.5.24
description: "Publish the merged 2026-05-24 fixes through the tag-driven GitHub release workflow, verify npm/npx/bunx/GitHub release surfaces, and record release evidence."
type: Chore
status: in_progress
priority: 0
tags[3]: npm,pm-cli,release
created_at: "2026-05-24T10:35:44.711Z"
updated_at: "2026-05-24T11:17:17.268Z"
assignee: codex-release
author: codex-release
parent: pm-rnpb
comments[9]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T10:36:39.110Z",codex-release,"Release preparation note: initial dry-run command refused to run because the working tree contained the newly created release tracker item; committing tracker setup first so the release pipeline can enforce its clean-tree guard."
  "2026-05-24T10:40:59.740Z",codex-release,"Evidence: pnpm release:pipeline:dry-run passed for 2026.5.24. Gate details included build, typecheck, docs/skills, static quality, coverage 108 files / 1623 tests / 100%, version policy, security scan, packed npx smoke, package-first dogfood 84 commands, npm pack, and release-note generation."
  "2026-05-24T10:53:00.086Z",codex-release,"Release workflow failure: GitHub run 26359132490 failed before npm publish at Reliability threshold gate. Logs show SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN was present but issue lookup returned sentry_api_403; SENTRY_PERSONAL_ADMIN_TOKEN was empty. This matches the documented split where release upload tokens may not have issue-read scope and the issue-threshold gate should skip without the personal admin token."
  "2026-05-24T10:53:33.739Z",codex-release,"Fix: updated .github/workflows/release.yml so the reliability issue-threshold gate skips when SENTRY_PERSONAL_ADMIN_TOKEN is absent, even if SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN exists for sourcemap upload. Focused shell check with SENTRY_AUTH_TOKEN=dummy and no personal token skips successfully."
  "2026-05-24T11:00:14.617Z",codex-release,"Fix verification: focused workflow contract test passed after updating tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts for the new SENTRY_PERSONAL_ADMIN_TOKEN skip message: PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts (1 file, 4 tests)."
  "2026-05-24T11:08:21.404Z",codex-release,"Publish failure: GitHub run 26359418647 reached npm publish after all gates passed, but npm returned E404 Not Found - PUT while NODE_AUTH_TOKEN was set from NPM_TOKEN. This indicates the token shadowed Trusted Publishing and lacked publish rights. Fixing release.yml to rely on OIDC Trusted Publishing and documenting the token-shadowing risk."
  "2026-05-24T11:08:34.836Z",codex-release,"Fix verification: focused workflow contract test passed after removing NODE_AUTH_TOKEN from the publish step and documenting Trusted Publishing: PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts (1 file, 4 tests)."
  "2026-05-24T11:17:05.611Z",codex-release,"Publish failure follow-up: run 26359584948 still showed NODE_AUTH_TOKEN in the publish environment despite removing explicit step env, likely from setup-node/npmrc. Updating publish step to unset NODE_AUTH_TOKEN/NPM_TOKEN and delete the registry auth token from NPM_CONFIG_USERCONFIG before npm publish --provenance so Trusted Publishing OIDC is not shadowed."
  "2026-05-24T11:17:17.268Z",codex-release,"Fix verification: focused workflow contract test passed after adding explicit token cleanup before npm publish: PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts (1 file, 4 tests)."
